---
Source:
  - Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
    ISBN: 978-1571746931
Page: 180
Author: Wang Wei
---
In happiness I wander these mountains alone.
All I understand is joy.
I walk along until the water ends
and then sit awhile to watch the clouds.
Should I happen to meet an old woodworker
we may talk and laugh awhile,
getting totally lost to time.
